&lt;h1 id="prop62"&gt;Prop62&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;November 2016&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re a California voter, there is an important proposition on your ballot this year: Proposition 62, which bans the death penalty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I was younger I used to think the debate about the death penalty was about when it&amp;rsquo;s ok to take a human life. Is it ok to kill a killer?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>